PrecisAcceptance of an Instrument (AMENDMENT OF DESIGNATION) wherein the LITTLE SHUSWAP LAKE BAND OF INDIANS amends a Designation made in 1991 with respect to certain parts of QUAAOUT INDIAN RESERVE NO. 1 in British Columbia, by extending its duration (from June 6, 2066 to December 31, 2080) and by expanding on the kind of things the Designated Lands may be used for.
